dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents zoning for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, "Shawano_Zoning_2017.gdb". [Zoning coverage showing the areas that fall under the jurisdiction of the Shawano County zoning ordinance.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Information provided in support of a request for certification of a farmland preservation zoning ordinance.]
